Stuff our website should allow us to do	
	
Login	
Register	
Ask Questions (provide form with send btn)	
	
Play Music	
	Comment on Music, autogenerate links from time signs in comments to start playing song at that particular time
	
	
	
Rate Music	
Tag Music (hashtags)	
	
Download Muisc (different file extensions)	
Upload Music -> give suggestions if musics already in the database	
	> enter meta data automatically (extract from music file)
	
Comment on stuff!	
	Like Songs, User Profiles, Playlists, whatever else we come up with
Delete Comments or at least make them disappear from timeline and report to admin	
Rate comments? Like +1 | 0	
	
Edit Profile Details	
	Username, Password, Date of Birth, Profile Picture
	whatever other details you may want the world to see
	Change Settings (e.g. whether other people can follow you, can find you in search, can comment on your profile, edit your blacklist)
	Change Settings again (e.g. themes or custom colours for stuff i.e. all my hashtags will be PURPLE!)
	> whether people can comment on/ rate your songs/playlists in general (individually setable in song's/playlist's details)
	set/change backup email address
	
	
	
	
	
Edit Song Details	
	Song Name, Artist, Picture, Album, Description
	Settings (e.g. enable/disable comments, enable/disable rating)
	decide hashtags
	
Look at other people's profiles	
	Comment on them, (request) follow, put on blacklist, report them to admin
	
Be notified (e.g. of people who want to follow me)	
	
Create Playlists, add songs and other playlists to them	
Comment on Playlists, Report Playlist, Add PL Picture, Description, hashtags	
Download Playlists (only own), delete playlists (own), edit playlists (own ..) 	
Rate Playlists	
	
Search	by hashtags, in songs, in users, in playlists, in all, in music (both songs and playlists), by artists whatever
	
Ask the user if they want to open the player in a new window so that music continuously plays even if the page is changed	
	
Personal History/Timeline	
